Preconditions:
The input parameter tasks must be a 2-dimensional array.
The tasks array must not be null.
The tasks array must have at least one row and one column.
Each element in the tasks array must be a non-negative integer.

Postconditions:
The method should return an integer value representing the minimum time required to complete all tasks.
The returned minimum time should be a non-negative integer.
The computer should be turned on for the entire duration of the minimum time.
All tasks in the tasks array should be completed within the minimum time.